06:52.256 --> 06:55.673
the insult of Christ, the insult of innocence

06:56.007 --> 07:00.090
openly done, sometimes legally accepted.

07:01.132 --> 07:05.132
So when we are born under such horrible circumstances,

07:05.381 --> 07:07.506
we have to build up

07:07.715 --> 07:10.464
a great force, ourselves,

07:10.840 --> 07:13.631
of spirituality.

