Then Shri Ganesh,

15:16.631 --> 15:18.673
He will never forgive these people -

15:18.882 --> 15:21.381
never, never, never.

15:21.590 --> 15:23.756
First of all, He'll expose them,

15:24.423 --> 15:28.506
